- [ ] RLS enabled with both tenant + warehouse access policies
- [ ] `stamp_tenant_id` trigger attached
- [ ] `updated_at` auto-update trigger attached
- [ ] Soft delete columns if rows will ever be "removed"
- [ ] Index on `(tenant_id, warehouse_id)` + primary filter column
